text:
I have never been in love 
Is it that easy? 
To be "in" love ?
Nope , 
It's the most miserably beautiful thing ;
A human is capable of .....
Miserably beautiful ;
Happily painful;
Peacefully chaotic ;
Securely scared ;
Hateful yet lovable ;
ALL THIS THINGS 
AT THE SAME TIME 
I BET 
ITS DIFFICULT YET SIMPLE
TO LOVE...

"STAY;
I don't want you to leave ..
BREATH ;
I want you to feel ...
CRY;
I like how your nose changes to a 
Fresh red tomato!
SCREAM;
you will have your catharsis..
FIGHT;
or I will provoke you 
And you don't want the ruin of urself..
WALK;
cause , It's dumb
To stay , where you don't belong !
RUN;
Everyone is chasing something here..
Welcome to the madHOUSE!
DANCE;
Come on, u deserve this 
Show us your moves!!
SMILE;
You have an intimidatingly glorious and a dangerously peaceful smile ..
LAUGH;
It's the most happiness has to offer
Keep it 
Happiness doesn't show kindness ..
It's not a giver ...
BREAK ;
What? I won't leave you out ! 
I love you and ( I won't spare you)
SCATTER ;
That's how it is nowadays ..
Don't flatter yourself ..
CHOKE;
Oh! You are in for some adventure 
Have fun!!
DIE ;
and 
Dead
The 
END."
